In the Matter of Dakota Fermin ZARATE Jacob Daniel Zarate. No. 616P03. Supreme Court of North Carolina. February 5, 2004. Janet K. Ledbetter, Hillsborough, for Burns. Jamie L. Hamlett, for Alamance DSS. Robert E. Collins, Guardian ad Litem, Attorney Adv., for Zarates.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed by Respondent on the 25th day of November 2003 in this matter for a writ of certiorari to review the order of the North Carolina Court of Appeals, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the North Carolina Court of Appeals:

"Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 5th day of February 2004."
